Simple. Easy. Hits the spot when you need a cereal vape before running out the door. &#xD;
&#xD;
While this simple cereal treat is no "Pebbles" by a longshot, when I need a cereal vape, 9 times out of 10 I'm gonna be making this because it's stupid simple and Pebbles has too many damn flavorings. Ain't nobody got time for that!
